{"type":"message","id":"4e72e0dc","parentId":"7fe7c7c0","timestamp":"2026-05-10T09:27:34.716Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me create the skill files manually based on what I read from the ClawHub page.\n","thinkingSignature":"744cc72219e56c582b91faa41276ef2893e015e37d2b16c1cad0517918411269"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_z3paekrsguxb_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\nname: rtk-integration\ndescription: Use RTK (Rust Token Killer) to reduce LLM token consumption by 60-90% on shell commands. Use when executing terminal commands, git operations, builds, tests, or any command that produces verbose output.\nlocation: ~/.openclaw/skills/rtk-integration\n---\n\n# RTK Integration\n\nRTK filters and compresses shell command outputs before they reach the LLM context window. Works with any agent/model — model-agnostic.\n\n## Setup\n\n### 1. Install RTK (if not already)\n```bash\ncurl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/rtk-ai/rtk/refs/heads/master/install.sh | sh\necho 'export PATH=\"$HOME/.local/bin:$PATH\"' >> ~/.bashrc && source ~/.bashrc\n```\n\n### 2. Verify\n```bash\nrtk --version && rtk gain\n```\n\n## Core Rule: Always Use RTK Prefixes\n\nWhen executing shell commands, always prefer RTK version over raw command. RTK adds <10ms overhead and reduces output by 60-90%.\n\n## Quick Reference\n\n### Files\n- `rtk ls .`\n- `rtk read <file>`\n- `rtk grep \"<pattern>\" .`\n- `rtk find \"*.ts\" .`\n- `rtk diff file1 file2`\n\n### Git (most impactful — use on EVERY git operation)\n- `rtk git status`\n- `rtk git diff`\n- `rtk git log -n 10`\n- `rtk git add .` → outputs just \"ok\"\n- `rtk git commit -m \"msg\"` → outputs \"ok <hash>\"\n- `rtk git push` → outputs \"ok main\"\n- `rtk git pull`\n\n### Tests — show failures only (-90%)\n- `rtk test npm test`\n- `rtk test npx jest`\n- `rtk vitest run`\n- `rtk playwright test`\n- `rtk pytest`\n- `rtk go test`\n- `rtk cargo test`\n\n### Build & lint\n- `rtk tsc`\n- `rtk next build`\n- `rtk lint`\n- `rtk lint biome`\n- `rtk cargo build`\n- `rtk cargo clippy`\n- `rtk ruff check .`\n\n### Docker\n- `rtk docker ps`\n- `rtk docker logs <container>`\n\n### Package managers\n- `rtk pnpm install`\n- `rtk npm install`\n\n### Check token savings\n```bash\nrtk gain\n```","path":"/home/apinan/.openclaw/skills/rtk-integration/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":94,"output":611,"cacheRead":49152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49857,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778405236076,"responseId":"064f827560bbec57c1df6209a8945b78"}}
