{"type":"message","id":"2a58afca","parentId":"56bd9eb4","timestamp":"2026-05-10T09:27:49.516Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"RTK is installed and working. Let me verify the skill is in the right place and test it.\n","thinkingSignature":"8a661ec0fdfdcfeb8a63bd97867efb11168a477853aa64fa9807de7545fe6042"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n🧑🏼‍💻 **ติดตั้งเสร็จแล้วครับเจ้านาย!**\n\n**สิ่งที่ทำ:**\n1. ✅ ติดตั้ง RTK v0.39.0 แล้ว (`~/.local/bin/rtk`)\n2. ✅ สร้าง skill `~/.openclaw/skills/rtk-integration/SKILL.md`\n3. ✅ verify ได้ `rtk 0.39.0`\n\n**วิธีใช้:** แทนที่จะรัน `git status` ให้รัน `rtk git status` แทน — output จะถูกบีบอัด ประหยัด token 60-90%\n\n**ดูผลประหยัด:** `rtk gain`\n\nผมจะเริ่มใช้ RTK ตั้งแต่คำสั่งถัดไปเลยครับ 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":103,"output":289,"cacheRead":49856,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50248,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778405258357,"responseId":"064f828b77c7aa6f0138bc180efa7960"}}
